overview:
If you are moving to or from anywhere in California, we can help you find movers and help you with everything you might need when moving.

UAC Moving Company California is more than just an affordable high quality moving and storage partner company in the State of California. We are a high quality professional moving and storage referral company that is a full service moving partner provider around California.

Our goal at UAC Moving Company California is to make sure your move goes as smooth as possible. We work hard to put you in contact with the best movers and relocation companies. Whether you are moving across town or across the country, we are here to provide the tools you need so you can experience a smooth relocation. Our moving companies that serve California are full service moving and storage companies. We provide our customers with experienced and courteous relocation professionals, clean, fully equipped, modern moving trucks and a full line of packing supplies.
